1
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:22,200
Who's there?

2
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:53,440
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 4]

3
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,360
Let me see your past.

4
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:18,040
What are you doing?

5
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,120
Don't be afraid.

6
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,600
I won't hurt you.

7
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,000
It was wrong

8
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:36,080
of those junior disciples
from the immortal sects.

9
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,800
I apologize on their behalf.

10
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,560
Please don't hold it against them.

11
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,560
This is the Jade Nectar
from the immortal realm.

12
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:46,760
It works wonders
for recovering internal injuries.

13
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,320
I see.

14
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,320
Now it's easy.

15
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,240
I'm almost recovered now.

16
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,040
I told you,

17
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,800
men and women should maintain propriety.

18
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,720
You can't sleep in the same room as me.

19
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,560
I only let you stay in my room before

20
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,160
was because you...

21
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,840
Because you were sick.

22
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,600
I only had you sleep in this room

23
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,360
so I could take care of you.

24
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:37,440
I won't!

25
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,560
Now

26
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,640
you've learned some immortal arts

27
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,320
and how to control yourself.

28
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:46,360
Tomorrow,

29
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:47,560
I'll prepare

30
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,240
a room for you.

31
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,440
From now on,
you'll have to live on your own.

32
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,320
I'm doing this for your own good.

33
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,560
That's my ingredient.

34
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,000
What?

35
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,720
You won't even let me eat a carrot?

36
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,040
Here.

37
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,720
I'm leaving.

38
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,400
Put that down!

39
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,000
Such beautiful flowers.

40
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,160
I'm glad you like them.

41
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,720
Every flower here
has a different fragrance

42
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,200
with its own unique effect.

43
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,760
Like this one.

44
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,760
Its scent is sweet and pleasant.

45
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,520
It can lift your spirits

46
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,240
and help you sleep.

47
00:03:59,520 --> 00:03:59,920
Here.

48
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:00,960
Take a sniff.

49
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:04,000
Smells nice.

50
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,440
And this one.

51
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:12,240
Actually, the true effect
of this flower's scent

52
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,000
is to make people feel smitten.

53
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,160
Yaoyang, come smell this.

54
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,320
This flower is so fragrant.

55
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,760
I'm hungry.

56
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,560
Yuxun.

57
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,520
Is there any food left?

58
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,440
Yes.

59
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,120
Ruoxi,

60
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,200
how about

61
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,040
we put this flower in the bedroom?

62
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,120
Great work.

63
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,200
Freshly washed fruit.

64
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,760
What are you writing?

65
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:22,720
Yaoyang

66
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,320
made me write the mantra
a hundred times.

67
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,760
Why

68
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,400
is Yaoyang so strict?

69
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,120
He is a bit strict.

70
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,440
Little Fox is much nicer.

71
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,520
Do you

72
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,360
like him?

73
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,800
What is

74
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,720
"like"?

75
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,400
"Like"

76
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,120
is when you want to

77
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,560
be with someone every day.

78
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,720
Every day?

79
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,520
Want to be with them every day?

80
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,360
I do want that!

81
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,160
Then you like him.

82
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,260
I also want to

83
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:58,320
be with Yaoyang every day.

84
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,840
I like Yaoyang too.

85
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,120
Looks like you really don't understand
romantic feelings.

86
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,760
So

87
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,840
what are romantic feelings like?

88
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,200
Romantic feelings

89
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,760
are something

90
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,760
you grasp intuitively,
not something easily explained.

91
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:15,880
I have

92
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,400
a rare book here.

93
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,360
Take a look.

94
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,520
This is a rare book.

95
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,000
You'll understand once you finish it.

96
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,640
Neither red

97
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,120
nor green.

98
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,160
[Neither Red nor Green. Guess the Word.]

99
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,040
Guess the world.

100
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,360
What does this mean?

101
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,160
You'll understand it in time.

102
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,320
Then I'll ask Yaoyang.

103
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:38,800
Stop right there!

104
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,920
Some people

105
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,600
understand this book,

106
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,200
and some just don't.

107
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,000
Yaoyang

108
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,400
might not get it.

109
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:50,720
Then who does?

110
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,720
Little Fox.

111
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,720
He's experienced and knowledgeable.

112
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,840
You could ask him.

113
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,840
You can even

114
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,920
seek his advice when needed.

115
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:58,960
Right.

116
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,040
Tu Jing.

117
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,080
Little Mushroom said

118
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,040
you know about this book.

119
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,400
[Neither Red nor Green. Guess the Word.]
He wants you to teach me.

120
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:16,960
Well...

121
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:19,760
This...

122
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,720
What does it mean, really?

123
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,320
Take a look.

124
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,760
Ruoxi,

125
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,960
we'll go over this book

126
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,640
another time.

127
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,600
Okay.

128
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,200
Then I'll put it away for now.

129
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,600
Oh no.

130
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,120
I forgot to prepare herbs for Yaoyang.

131
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,320
I have to go do that.

132
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,200
I'll be back later.

133
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,360
Yuxun

134
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,880
is unbelievable.

135
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,680
Look at this.

136
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,760
This is a method from an immortal book.

137
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,720
It's supposed to help restore
your inner energy.

138
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,320
You should soak for a bit longer.

139
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,520
Earlier,

140
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:19,880
your mind was damaged.

141
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:23,280
This herbal bath will help you
restore your energy and calm your mind.

142
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:24,640
Ever since...

143
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,320
I haven't had a herbal bath
in a long time.

144
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,240
Thank you.

145
00:08:36,540 --> 00:08:37,660
Then go ahead and soak now.

146
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:39,360
I have to go study with Tu Jing.

147
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,360
Tonight, I'll let you two enjoy

148
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,960
a romantic, sleepless night.

149
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,760
There's one herb left.

150
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,520
Oh no!

151
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:05,360
Get out.

152
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,440
But there's one herb missing.

153
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,760
Are you alright?

154
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,360
Close your eyes.

155
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:53,800
When...

156
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,600
When can I open them?

157
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,560
Count...

158
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,760
Count to ten.

159
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:00,720
Are you

160
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,920
mad at me?

161
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,360
One.

162
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:07,920
Two.

163
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:09,920
Three.

164
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:38,480
♪What is flickering?♪

165
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:41,220
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

166
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:47,220
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

167
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:50,100
♪What is falling?♪

168
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:53,340
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

169
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:58,780
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

170
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:01,300
♪When petals drift down♪

171
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:02,800
♪When the rain falls all around♪

172
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:05,500
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

173
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:07,360
♪Beyond the dunes♪

174
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:08,740
♪No end in sight♪

175
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:11,740
♪I am like a mayfly♪

176
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:13,300
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

177
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:14,800
♪Nor will I run away♪

178
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:17,760
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

179
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:23,020
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

180
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:40,080
♪What is flickering?♪

181
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,780
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

182
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:48,780
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

183
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:52,020
♪What is falling?♪

184
00:11:52,140 --> 00:11:54,960
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

185
00:11:55,180 --> 00:12:00,180
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

186
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:02,780
♪When petals drift down♪

187
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:04,280
♪When the rain falls all around♪

188
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:06,940
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
